986c8da3bc587ff831df6fdaea3fdb2cf9","tid":563004,"uid":155353,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係幾好，但如果故障是旦跌粒落地球都死傷慘重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>無知一問，衛星唔係無重狀態咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我唔知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但之前唔係傳支那死左果粒有機會墜落黎咩</blockquote>衛星其實離地球唔算遠 都係有地球重力拉緊佢落去<br />\n只不過因為衛星本身有慣性動力所以一直都keep住係太空<br />\n詳細等physic人答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔關慣性事 衛星係太空做既係圓周運動 個方向一直變 又點會係慣性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之所以唔會跌落去係因係佢既引力比左去做向心力做圓周運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n圓周運動向心力-&gt;F=mv^2/r<br />\n而個F 由重力（gravity)提供<br />\n人地計過數以咩速度行粒衛星就唔會跌去唔會飛走<br />\n呢d 中學生都識計既數人地咁大間公司點會唔識計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢地係用相對論計既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859204061121dbc4484fd5f4e9a37aa84a11a41b","tid":563004,"uid":141116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0449c3d543b3c3890565ed8b674e3591b924055f","tid":563004,"uid":47042,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d63f597aef17c89aa14eccc40cf1a097e681567b","tid":563004,"uid":84265,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c4a9c10f1f179bc9f848d7c7e6b94e328edff9bb","tid":563004,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T18:52:50.000Z","msg":"衛星其實離地球唔算遠 都係有地球重力拉緊佢落去<br />\n只不過因為衛星本身有慣性動力所以一直都keep住係太空<br />\n詳細等physic人答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T20:04:48.000Z","msg":"中學生都答到你呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma